Information Retrieval API
=================================

This project consists of a number of proxies, searching for results in a list of widely-known websites, such as CNN, NYT etc. 
Based on Play Framework (MVC), in Java, the proxies are created as Controllers, returning the first 10 results' data from the specific
website, regarding the HTTP request, in a map of JSON objects. The data, the map contains for each result, in case of existence, 
are the following:
  - Title
  - Summary
  - URL
  - Image (URL)
  - Date
